
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Training";
}

<h1>Training</h1>

<div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                DotNet Training
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                The .NET track focuses on building scalable enterprise applications using the Microsoft ecosystem, which is a core partnership for the firm.

                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Core Fundamentals:</strong> C# language deep-dive, including OOPs, Async/Await, and LINQ.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Web Development:</strong> ASP.NET Core MVC and <strong>Web API</strong> development for enterprise services.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Database & Data:</strong> SQL Server integration using <strong>Entity Framework Core</strong> (EF Core).
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Frontend Integration:</strong> Building modern UIs by pairing .NET backends with <strong>Angular</strong> or <strong>React</strong>.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Cloud Deployment:</strong> Introduction to hosting and scaling applications on <strong>Microsoft Azure</strong>.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>  
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                Testing
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                The Testing track focuses on Capgemini's <strong>Quality Engineering</strong> approach, shifting from manual verification to automated, AI-driven validation.

                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Methodologies:</strong> Training in <strong>TMAP®</strong> (Capgemini's industry-leading methodology) and Agile Testing.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Automation Suite:</strong> Mastering Selenium with Java/Python and the Robot Framework.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Performance & Load:</strong> Using JMeter and K6 to ensure application stability under enterprise stress.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>CI/CD Integration:</strong> Automating test execution within Azure DevOps and GitLab pipelines.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>AI in Testing:</strong> Leveraging GenAI to automate test case generation and self-healing scripts.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                Python and Django Training
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
                The Django track centers on rapid, secure web development using Python, often integrated with AI and data-driven enterprise solutions.

                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Python Mastery:</strong> Advanced Python concepts including Decorators, Generators, and Multithreading.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Architecture:</strong> Deep dive into MVT (Model-View-Template) and project scaffolding.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>RESTful Services:</strong> Building robust APIs using the <strong>Django REST Framework (DRF)</strong>.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Database & ORM:</strong> Managing complex data models and migrations with Django’s built-in ORM.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Modern Integration:</strong> Connecting Django with GenAI models (LangChain) and containerization with Docker.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>